msgid "Adds the full automation template library (database), sequences, and send logs on the Email screen. Everyone already gets Delivery settings plus the four core customer templates (booking, payment, cancellation, reminder) without this module."
msgstr ""

#: app/Core/Modules/ModuleManager.php:105
msgid "Customize booking form fields with drag-and-drop builder. Add custom fields for traveler information and emergency contacts. Create the perfect booking experience for your customers."
msgstr ""

#: app/Core/Modules/ModuleManager.php:119
msgid "Advanced Discount"
msgstr ""

#: app/Core/Modules/ModuleManager.php:120
msgid "Create group discounts that auto-apply based on traveler count. Combine promo codes with group savings for maximum flexibility and conversion optimization."
msgstr ""

#: app/Core/Modules/ModuleManager.php:134
msgid "Automatically sync customers to Mailchimp lists when they book. Add tags based on trips booked. Build targeted email campaigns and nurture leads effectively."
msgstr ""

#: app/Core/Modules/ModuleManager.php:149
msgid "Track booking conversions with Facebook Pixel. Retarget visitors who viewed trips. Optimize ad campaigns with accurate conversion data and build lookalike audiences."
msgstr ""

#: app/Core/Modules/ModuleManager.php:164
msgid "Enhanced e-commerce tracking for GA4. Track view_item, begin_checkout, and purchase events. Server-side tracking via Measurement Protocol for accurate conversion data."
msgstr ""

#: app/Core/Modules/ModuleManager.php:179
msgid "Enable deposit and partial payment options for bookings. Allow customers to pay a percentage upfront and the rest later. Perfect for high-value trips and improving conversion rates."
msgstr ""

#: app/Core/Modules/ModuleManager.php:194
msgid "Automatically schedule the remaining booking balance after a partial or deposit payment. Uses your payment gateway (e.g. Stripe) to invoice or charge on the dates you configure."
msgstr ""

#: app/Core/Modules/ModuleManager.php:209
msgid "Automatically adjust trip prices based on demand, seasonality, early bird discounts, and last-minute deals. Maximize revenue with intelligent pricing rules that respond to booking patterns."
msgstr ""

#: app/Core/Modules/ModuleManager.php:223
msgid "Custom Landing Pages"
msgstr ""

#: app/Core/Modules/ModuleManager.php:224
msgid "Point destinations, activities, and trip types to any WordPress page. Use your page builder and Yatra shortcodes on that page; catalog links and redirects use the page URL when the module is enabled."
msgstr ""

#: app/Core/Modules/ModuleManager.php:239
msgid "Recover lost sales by automatically tracking abandoned bookings and sending targeted email sequences. Win back customers who left before completing their purchase."
msgstr ""

#: app/Core/Modules/ModuleManager.php:254
msgid "Fully rebrand Yatra as your own product. Replace the plugin name, logo, author, support URL, and email/PDF branding shown to clients. Available exclusively on the Agency plan."
msgstr ""

#: app/Core/Modules/ModuleManager.php:270
msgid "Generate trip descriptions, itineraries, SEO meta, and email copy without leaving the editor. Inline AI affordances on every long-text field — write less, finish more. Bring your own OpenAI or Anthropic key."
msgstr ""

#: app/Core/Modules/ModuleManager.php:271
msgid "Productivity"
msgstr ""

#: app/Core/Modules/ModuleManager.php:286
msgid "Send booking confirmations, payment alerts, departure reminders, and review requests over WhatsApp — the channel customers actually read. Inbound messages route into your Yatra Enquiries inbox. Bring your own WhatsApp Business / Cloud API credentials; messages are billed by Meta, not by the plugin."
msgstr ""

#: app/Core/Modules/ModuleManager.php:287
msgid "Communications"
msgstr ""

#: app/Core/Modules/ModuleManager.php:302
msgid "Sync your trips + departures + inventory to Viator, GetYourGuide, Klook, and TripAdvisor Experiences. Pull bookings back into Yatra as native bookings. Real-time inventory sync prevents oversells across channels. Per-channel pricing offsets cover OTA commission. The single biggest revenue lever for tour operators on multiple platforms."
msgstr ""

#: app/Core/Modules/ModuleManager.php:303
msgid "Distribution"
msgstr ""

#: app/Core/Modules/ModuleManager.php:318
msgid "Push every Yatra event (booking, payment, refund, customer, enquiry, trip, departure) to your CRM, accounting tool, Zapier, Make, Slack, or any HTTPS endpoint. HMAC-SHA256 signed payloads, automatic retry with exponential backoff, full delivery log with payload inspection + replay, per-endpoint encrypted secrets. The integration backbone for agencies wiring Yatra into a custom tech stack."
msgstr ""

